Looking for a quick and delicious toast recipe? Here’s a whipped cottage cheese toast with pear and basil using @liyamehl’s homemade sourdough! It’s easy, delicious and will leave you feeling great and satisfied. 

You need: 
1/4 cup cottage cheese, blended in a food processor 
1/2 pear, sliced 
2 tbsp basil leaves, sliced 
Balsamic glaze or vinegar
Finishing salt 

Toast your sourdough. Spread a generous amount of whipped cottage cheese on toast and add pears. Add basil. Drizzle with balsamic and sprinkle on finishing salt!
